Help Type: command
Command: wikigraph wkg-job://<job-id> boost

Purpose:
  Move one queued job to the front of the queue.

Usage:
  wikigraph wkg-job://<job-id> boost

Arguments:
  <job-id>              Full job id or an unambiguous prefix.

Behavior:
  - Boosting only applies to queued jobs.
  - Boosting does not preempt running jobs.

Example:
  wikigraph wkg-job://75d12f7e boost
